# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  LinkedIn SDR Agent — Cron Schedule Example
#
#  Install:
#    1. Edit this file with your project path
#    2. Run: crontab crontab.example
#
#  Or add manually:
#    crontab -e
#    # Then paste the line below (adjust path as needed)
#
#  Logs go to: data/logs/pipeline_YYYY-MM-DD.log
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Daily at 8:00 AM ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Runs the full pipeline every morning
0 8 * * * /path/to/your/project/pipeline/run_daily.sh

# ── Alternative schedules ──────────────────────────────────────
# Every day at 6:00 AM
# 0 6 * * * /path/to/your/project/pipeline/run_daily.sh

# Weekdays only at 8:00 AM
# 0 8 * * 1-5 /path/to/your/project/pipeline/run_daily.sh

# Every 12 hours
# 0 8,20 * * * /path/to/your/project/pipeline/run_daily.sh

# ── Quick install (adjust path) ────────────────────────────────
# PROJECT="/home/yourname/projects/leadgen-agent"
# (crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo "0 8 * * * $PROJECT/pipeline/run_daily.sh") | crontab -
